node.text:
A little bit of #LuckyHistory 🍀📚. 

In 2012 we released the Lucky “Motion” deck which ran 4.25in wide X 20.5in long, and was the center piece for our Lucky “Strata” Complete. This scooter was one step up from our original Lucky “CREW” complete at the time, and is now the equivalent, in regards to proportions, to our 2021 Lucky Covenant Complete. Would you have ridden the Lucky Motion Deck? 🤔 #Scooter #Scootering #VintageScooter #TheMoreYouKnow
